    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "okay i get the tapering thing. but if i'm tapering off the zoloft, can i start taking a little bit of the st john's wort while i'm still on the lower doses to help with the transition? i just want to make sure i don't have a gap where my anxiety spikes. like, is it safe to have them both in my system for a bit while i switch over?",
